Description: Lightweight Twitter Client base on Gtk2 and Webkit.
 Lightweight Twitter Client base on Gtk2 and Webkit.
 .
 Features include:
   - Update/View Timelines.
   - Follow/Unfollow peoples.
   - Post status.
   - Reply tweets.
   - Post direct messages.
   - View people profile.
   - Native notification.
   - Global key-shortcut.

